{"tid":1668304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"水警自殺單野好多疑點?","createTime":"2019-10-22T02:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:40:43.000Z","uid":5299,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1f82c20873ab56eab935c1dea0003b1d9613fa65","tid":1668304,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"呢單野好多傳媒有報, 但如果睇曬既話, 就發現好多出入, 唔排除係我多疑, 不過烏犬而家冇人信:<br />\n<br />\n1. 有冇病?<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/pc/article/P1gkao?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Fpc%2Farticle%2FP1gkao%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=49449b08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/pc/article/P1gkao?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n星島話有癌魔折騰, 其他報導冇提, 仲要失更, 真心一問癌魔折騰既POPO仲要番工咩?<br />\n<br />\n2. 燒炭架車唔係事主, 烏犬話冇可疑<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191022%2F00176_053.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=76eda411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html</a><br />\n死者姓何<br />\n涉事私家車登記車主為姓梁男子弟(即係唔係佢老婆)<br />\n<br />\n東方記者點解會提呢樣野? 良心HINTS? 別有內情?<br />\n<br />\n3. 有冇遺書?<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191022%2F00176_053.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=76eda411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/1022/364100.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2019%2F1022%2F364100.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=5eab41d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/1022/364100.html</a><br />\n文匯就藍屍MODE ON, 咩都關佔中事, 可以不理<br />\n<br />\n東方:有檢獲遺書<br />\n文匯: 未有檢獲遺書<br />\n<br />\n4. 佢老婆有冇到現場?<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191022%2F00176_053.html&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=76eda411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191022/00176_053.html</a><br />\n何兩名男女親友接獲消息後，到場了解情況，兩人均神情哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n兩名男女親友係咪又係臨記? 點解冇寫佢老婆黎?<br />\n<br />\n5. 屍體正確發現地點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5287887-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%A0%AA%E7%97%85%E7%A3%A8-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F5287887-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A0%25AA%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%25A3%25A8-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2582%25AD%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ce413f8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5287887-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%A0%AA%E7%97%85%E7%A3%A8-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1</a><br />\n牛潭尾三十三號一個露天貨倉庫的場主，發現相識的何警長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2019/10/22/IN1910220007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F10%2F22%2FIN1910220007.htm&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=1e99768d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2019/10/22/IN1910220007.htm</a><br />\n有地盤保安員在落馬洲石湖圍路一處山路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xd4jXez.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxd4jXez.jpg&h=6631e5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差好遠啵!<br />\n<br />\n以上只係我歸納各報導所得, 未知真相, 求神探出手"},{"pid":"c21e83a97093b2c9fed57ffa48ec07c0dac0bbd1","tid":1668304,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"連登神探又有案可以查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc4ca3a923aab9f03eada38dc5a32f33fa94d51","tid":1668304,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21e83a97093b2c9fed57ffa48ec07c0dac0bbd1","tid":1668304,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"連登神探又有案可以查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"神探召喚"},{"pid":"132e45226075999583c88a93655461f157d677ad","tid":1668304,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"報夢巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d6b31b97cff8c466aa3fc5d153e6d9999fab64","tid":1668304,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"新方向 開返10個post洗版先"},{"pid":"c0aaa2c5ccf0d2945da798d783b7345213766ecf","tid":1668304,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:31:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏同我入嚟<br />\n想connect全世界同我入嚟<br />\n把握時機 食住個勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b724d55fe10dbadba20a00f72d04ae6992343d2","tid":1668304,"uid":256514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8f438ce4d05170793d7581ec6ffb7af121c8e64","tid":1668304,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T02:33:57.000Z","msg":"又唔係有核彈留低 死左唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"0e320035aeea914fd49e147c8a591cb23efe4c20","tid":1668304,"uid":137